Eph. 2:19-20
Fratres: Jam non estis hóspites et ádvenæ; sed estis cives Sanctórum et doméstici Dei, superædificáti super fundaméntum Apostolórum et Prophetárum, ipso summo angulári lápide Christo Jesu.
Brethren: Now you are no more strangers and foreigners; but you are fellow citizens with the Saints, and the domestics of God, built upon the foundation of the Apostles and Prophets, Jesus Christ himself being the chief corner stone.
